parameters: \n<Ameria>"Ah... we've finally made it out into the light..."

\n<Roselitte>"However, it looks like the sun is about to set. We should
prepare to camp soon."
\n<Roselitte>"No need to get so poetic and downhearted."
\n<Lyric>"Hey, Ameria. How much further is it to Anatos from here?"

\n<Ameria>"Hmm... I don't think it's too far. Direction-wise, it's
upstream from this river, so if we follow along, we should
get there soon."

\n<Lyric>"The thief also said we should follow along the river,
right? Does this river lead to Anatos?"

\n<Ameria>"Yes. There's a river that flows right beside Anatos, so I
think this is probably that river. So, maybe--"

\n<Roselitte>"My clothes got dirty in the cave... and there's sand in my
mouth..."
\n<Ameria>"Oh, um... we were discussing the location of Anatos."

\n<Lyric>"A river leading to Anatos, huh... Oh! Then maybe this river
is connected to that thing. Maybe that's where the secret
escape route is."

\n<Lyric>"The sewers. If this river leads to Anatos, then it must be
connected, right? Sewers are a classic for secret escape
routes."

\n<Lyric>"Ugh, this is the worst! My clothes are dirty now! Is there
some kind of rule that knights have to puke on me!?"
\n<Roselitte>"What on earth are you talking about... ugh..."
